The paper is about the design and deployment of wireless sensor networks, which falls under the category of networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the use of optimization algorithms for network design, which could fall under information theory (cs.IT) or control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of field evaluation and iterative processes, which could fall under distributed computing (cs.DC) or machine learning (cs.MA).
